author: @coreyms
text: This was my first live stream, so I expected some technical difficulties. It looks like this first one cut off the far right of my monitor, so you won't be able to see the complete questions I'm responding to. If you enjoy videos like this then I'll work on improving this format for you all. But I will still mostly be focusing on tutorials. If I do videos like this, they will be few and far between. Let me know what you think! And stay safe!  EDIT: For anyone who left a Superchat (paid live comment) that I didn't get around to answering, I am so so sorry! This was my first live stream and I will definitely prioritize those in the future. Thanks so much for your support and I'm sorry if I didn't get around to them! I didn't expect as many questions as I got, so I was doing my best. I will go back through and look at the superchats and answer them in a future video!
